{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4eaa227af2","title":"各地斗争分子应加人团体","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"702e2d7fce","index":0,"year":1936,"month":4,"day":3,"articleId":"4eaa227af2"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji8","name":"毛泽东全集第8卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji8.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji8":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"04fdeb504d","type":"paragraph","text":"各地斗争分子应加人团体口","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"4eaa227af2"},{"id":"96ef5ded69","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年4月3日）林、鼓、朱甲、新成立之地方独立团应暂随你们行动，加强其领导骨干建立党组织，继续扩大至四百人。乙、鉴于石楼居杀之教训，凡公开地方活动积极斗争之分子，应令其加入独立团游击队，转为游击战争骨干，同时将一切积极而未公开活动之分子转入秘密党与农会。内、责成你们在满县、大宁、百县地区建立第二个地方独立团、秘密的党与农会","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"4eaa227af2"},{"id":"2d045d72b5","type":"paragraph","text":"彭毛","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"4eaa227af2"},{"id":"bffe0db416","type":"paragraph","text":"四月三日1]这是毛泽东和红军第一方亩军司令员彭德怀给第一方而军常一军团","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"4eaa227af2"}],"page":{"id":"55fcb8cee2","publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"4eaa227af2","start":362,"end":362}}}},"__N_SSG":true}